Court International Criminal (Costa Rica);  
</b>146.9.<b> Speed up the process of accession to the ICESCR and ICCPR 
(Uruguay); 
</b>146.10.<b> Promptly complete the process of ratification of other fundamental 
instruments, in particular the ICCPR and ICESCR, and consider ratifying the 
