</b>146.115.<b> Move to discretionary sentencing for drug trafficking charges 
(United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland); 
</b>146.116.<b> Abolish death penalty for minors and drug dealers (Albania); 
</b>146.117.<b> Repeal compulsory death penalty and eliminate its application for 
